--How to Connect the Smart Stick to Blynk

1) Install the Blynk IoT App from the Play Store / App Store

2) Create a New Blynk Project and note your Auth Token

3) Set your mobile hotspot to 2.4 GHz network mode

4) Enter Wi-Fi name and password in the code (ssid & pass)

5) Paste the Auth Token into the Arduino code

6) Upload the code to the ESP8266 board

7) Power the device (USB or power bank)

8) Device will automatically connect to Blynk Cloud

9) Open the Blynk app to monitor alerts and notifications
